bunkers that are  only  a few hundred meters deep<br>
and that are directly below  below ground zero. <br>
<br>
2. Really deep bunkers require multimegaton H-bombs to either crush them  physicaly with earthquake like<br>
shocks or  to dry roast, or suffocate  those inside them.<br>
<br>
3. Free fall ballistic bombs , dropped by aircraft <br>
with impact fuzes, or with subsurface penetration<br>
 cones and time  fuzes are best for bunker busting.<br>
<br>
4. Ballistic  Missiles, and cruise misslies  can be used for this , but aircraft are best in orderto maximize accuracy, and precision of targeting <br>
<br>
<br>
5. The greater acuracy provided by planes makes it easier to achieve bunker busting with smaller - or lower  yield weapons.<br>
<br>
